changeSet.createView: SELECT taskinstan0_.token_ AS id_situacao_processo, pooledacto2_.actorid_ AS nm_pooled_actor, fluxo.id_fluxo, processdef6_.name_ AS nm_fluxo, task4_.name_ AS nm_tarefa, tj.id_tarefa, c.id_caixa, c.nm_caixa, proc.id_processo, taskinstan0_.procinst_ AS id_process_instance, taskinstan0_.id_ AS id_task_instance, taskinstan0_.task_ AS id_task, taskinstan0_.actorid_ AS nm_actorid FROM ((((((((((jbpm_taskinstance taskinstan0_ LEFT JOIN tb_tarefa_jbpm tj ON ((tj.id_jbpm_task = taskinstan0_.task_))) LEFT JOIN tb_tarefa tbtarefa ON ((tbtarefa.id_tarefa = tj.id_tarefa))) LEFT JOIN tb_fluxo fluxo ON ((fluxo.id_fluxo = tbtarefa.id_fluxo))) LEFT JOIN jbpm_taskactorpool pooledacto1_ ON ((taskinstan0_.id_ = pooledacto1_.taskinstance_))) LEFT JOIN jbpm_pooledactor pooledacto2_ ON ((pooledacto1_.pooledactor_ = pooledacto2_.id_))) RIGHT JOIN tb_processo proc ON ((proc.id_processo = ( SELECT DISTINCT ( SELECT DISTINCT longinstan1_.longvalue_ FROM jbpm_variableinstance longinstan1_ WHERE (((longinstan1_.class_ = 'L') AND ((longinstan1_.name_) = 'processo')) AND (longinstan1_.processinstance_ = longinstan3_.processinstance_))) AS longvalue_ FROM jbpm_variableinstance longinstan3_ WHERE (longinstan3_.token_ = taskinstan0_.token_))))) LEFT JOIN tb_caixa c ON ((proc.id_caixa = c.id_caixa))) LEFT JOIN jbpm_task task4_ ON ((taskinstan0_.task_ = task4_.id_))) LEFT JOIN jbpm_processinstance processins5_ ON ((taskinstan0_.procinst_ = processins5_.id_))) LEFT JOIN jbpm_processdefinition processdef6_ ON ((processins5_.processdefinition_ = processdef6_.id_))) WHERE (EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM ((jbpm_taskinstance taskinstan7_ LEFT JOIN jbpm_taskactorpool pooledacto8_ ON ((taskinstan7_.id_ = pooledacto8_.taskinstance_))) LEFT JOIN jbpm_pooledactor pooledacto9_ ON ((pooledacto8_.pooledactor_ = pooledacto9_.id_))), jbpm_task task10_ WHERE ((((taskinstan7_.task_ = task10_.id_) AND (taskinstan7_.issuspended_ = 0)) AND (taskinstan7_.isopen_ = 1)) AND (taskinstan0_.id_ = taskinstan7_.id_))))

changeSet.author: liquibase
changeSet.createView: SELECT ncf.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo, f.qt_prazo, ( SELECT avg(pe.nr_tempo_gasto) AS avg FROM tb_processo pr JOIN tb_processo_epa pe ON pr.id_processo=pe.id_processo JOIN tb_natureza_categoria_fluxo ncf ON ncf.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo=pe.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo WHERE pr.dt_fim IS NOT NULL AND ncf.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo = pe.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo GROUP BY pe.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo) AS nr_tempo_medio FROM tb_natureza_categoria_fluxo ncf JOIN tb_fluxo f ON (f.id_fluxo=ncf.id_fluxo)

changeSet.author: liquibase
changeSet.createView: SELECT tempostarefas.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo, tb_tarefa.id_tarefa, tb_tarefa.ds_tarefa, tb_tarefa.nr_prazo, tb_tarefa.tp_prazo, tempostarefas.nr_tempo_medio FROM (tb_tarefa JOIN ( SELECT p.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo, pet.id_tarefa, avg(pet.nr_tempo_gasto) AS nr_tempo_medio FROM (tb_processo_epa_tarefa pet JOIN tb_processo_epa p ON (pet.id_processo=p.id_processo)) WHERE ((NOT (pet.dt_fim IS NULL)) AND (pet.nr_tempo_gasto > 0)) GROUP BY pet.id_tarefa, p.id_natureza_categoria_fluxo) tempostarefas ON (tempostarefas.id_tarefa=tb_tarefa.id_tarefa))
